{
  "stem": "6878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were German soldiers amongst them, and I used to go in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody knew that I'm Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had a bit of chutzpah as to go for another helping-- take the tray and go for another helping.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that lasted for three weeks, and then we were transferred to another unit, which I couldn't go there anymore.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the Jewish people in ghetto were never starved of starvation if they wouldn't be shot, because everybody find a way how to get through with a little bit of product.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We used to take in-- one day they used to take away the-- the food from us, and the next day we carry again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was nonstop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certain times they used to give us a brick, kicking in our-- in our ass-- kicking us and go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on certain, they were quite harsh if they would find money or something like this, and we'll come back to money a little bit later, what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we worked on the airport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the airport used to come also Lithuanian farmers from the area, from around us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to bring some cement, bricks, this that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got in touch with the Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We start talking to them-- I start talking to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If one day we escape from the ghetto, if they will let us-- if they will help us a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, there are some of them yes, some no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are some people good ones, some bad ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So some of them, like a farmer said, you bring out your little boy, my wife-- I spoke to her-- she'll take him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And those days, the Germans used to deport kids from Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
